quran[23{c,v,t}:
89,1,qasam hai Fajar ki
89,2,aur das raton ki
89,3,aur juft aur taaq ki
89,4,aur raat ki jabkay woh rukhsat ho rahi ho
89,5,kya iss mein kisi sahib aqal ke liye koi qasam hai ?
89,6,tum ne dekha nahi ke tumahray Rab ne kya bartao kya
89,7,ounchay satonon walay Aad Iram ke sath
89,8,jin ke manind koi qoum duniya ke mulkon mein peda nahi ki gayi thi ?
89,9,aur samood ke sath jinhon ne waadi mein chatanein tarashi theen ?
89,10,aur menkhon walay firaon ke sath ?
89,11,yeh woh log thay jinhon ne duniya ke mulkon mein barri sar kashi ki thi
89,12,aur un mein bohat fasaad phelaya tha
89,13,aakhir kaar tumahray Rab ne un par azaab ka kora barsa diya
89,14,haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara Rab ghaat lagaye hue hai
89,15,magar ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke is ka Rab jab uss ko azmaish mein dalta hai aur ussay izzat aur Nemat deta hai to woh kehta hai ke mere Rab ne mujhe izzat daar bana diya
89,16,aur jab woh uss ko azmaish mein dalta hai aur uss ka rizaq uss par tang kar deta hai to woh kehta hai ke mere Rab ne mujhe zaleel kar diya
89,17,"hargiz nahi, balkay tum yateem se izzat ka sulooq nahi karte"
89,18,aur maskeen ko khana khilanay par aik dosray ko nahi aksate
89,19,aur meeras ka sara maal samaitt kar kha jatay ho
89,20,aur maal ki mohabbat mein buri terhan girftar ho
89,21,"hargiz nahi, jab zameen pay Dur pay coat coat kar raig zaar bana di jaye gi"
89,22,aur tumhara Rab jalva farma hoga iss haal mein ke farishtay saf Dur saf kharray hon ge
89,23,"aur jahannum uss roz samnay le aayi jaye gi, uss din ensaan ko samajh aeye gi aur is waqt uss ke samajhney ka kya haasil ?"
